{"tid":112030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲男金錢糾紛遭禁錮 警拘13歲男童","createTime":"2017-02-08T00:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T05:00:42.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f807ec83e31334c0611478acdc00f89b042dbf62","tid":112030,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:10:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>18歲男金錢糾紛遭禁錮 警拘13歲男童</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-08 06:30:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n凌晨1時許，一名19歲姓黎女子報警，指一名18歲姓黃男友人，在旺角上海街一單位，因金錢問題與數名男子爭執，並且被人禁錮；期間數名男子曾向黃恐嚇，聲稱要傷害他。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，拘捕一名13歲男童，涉嫌非法禁錮。案件列作非法禁錮、刑事恐嚇，交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。追緝涉案另三名男子，包括一名年約20至25歲，身高約1.7米，瘦身材；一名年約17至20歲，身高約1.7米，肥身材，案發時身穿白色上衣；一名年約18歲，身高約1.6米，瘦身材，案發時戴眼鏡。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3d17cfddfcb466d3e0e0ce76be48fa38f87d13","tid":112030,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6acc12679e0cc8aa8ad8f9270b7ffbe586cbe6ea","tid":112030,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:15:40.000Z","msg":"渣架"},{"pid":"29d14c0228d58f48101f945118dcba838b7c78e9","tid":112030,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾細路蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇睇內文"},{"pid":"e64d716f2f139820ef6fabbc79d631b8f0899cd2","tid":112030,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423b3089d729417514b2d40c214d68be2188f5c4","tid":112030,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:19:14.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"7d23a072793ad61f625d68167366b277b3f16005","tid":112030,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco